
hamare gaon mein aye khuda hai uska rang safed hai bahut is darta hai kaam aata hai
meenu ka ghar bahut bada hai ghar ke paas itwari hai waha bahut se phool khile hain full opare behti hai
bade achhe lagte hain burrows paatshala jata hai usse kavithai acche lagte hain sab ko kavithai sunata hai
pahad par ek payr hai paper ki daal hai ek daal par ek ghosla hai bhosle me it under hai
basant ka mahina hai rang birange phool khile hain bhavre mandra rahe hain behti hai
raju ke ghar main ek gaya gaya karam karna hai raju shoes cuz kehlata hai deti hai
chachi jungle jaate hain jungle se lakdi lagte hain lakdi bazar mai bichhde hain mere liye nahi pita will aate hain
ravi k pas aye khuda hi bharosa humne le jata hai kutta ghar ki rakhwali karta hai bahut pyar karta hai
mere shikshak bahut acche hai ye kabhi nahin aate hain mujhe pyar se samjhe aate hain se bada acha lagta hai
hamare ghar ke paas ek tha laga dala bahut sundar bada hai uske kinare rang birange phool khile hain bahut sahi hai
subah subah hui hai jaan ke khet mein paani bhar gaya hai
mere chacha ji ki chaal hai khet mai janu gaate hai jab barish hone lagti hai jaan ka paida hota hai